$aarPowDefensive = [
	"body armor (artificial)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX possesses artificially-created armor that provides protection and possibly a way of possessing other Powers. Armor comes in many forms of exotic plate-mail, nuclear-powered exoskeletons, or mechanically-created force fields.</p>

	<p>NOTE: The player should work with the Mods to create armor which properly represents your character, and fits the look and feel of our game. The player can also determine which Powers are possessed by XXXXcharnameXXXX and which are properties of the armor. Any powers built into the armor can later be modified and enhanced; think of the changes Tony Stark has made iover the years to the Iron Man armor. On the other hand, powers that are built into the armor may possibly suffer from mechanical failure. The Armor&#39;s Power rank determines its durability and ability to resist/reduce damage.</p>",


	"force field" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX possesses the ability to generate a protective barrier around  XXXXcharnameXXXX which is proof against a wide variety of forces, including brute force, energy attacks and extreme temperature conditions. It can be projected and or used for a variety of feats.</p>

	<p>The force field completely absorbs any and all damage which might be caused by attack which is equal to or less in Intensity than that of the fields Power Rank. If The Intensity of the attack is higher than that of the field, then the attack is reduced by the fields power rank. The remaining Intensity breaches the field and affects anyone within by This diminished effect.</p>",


	"reflection" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can turn any attack sent against them back onto the attacker. The attack may be of any nature: brute force, Power, or even magic. The Power absorbs the energy of the attack equal to or less then it&#39;s intensity rank and redirects it back at  XXXXcharnameXXXX would attacker. If the attack&#39;s Intensity is higher that of XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s eflection power rank, some of the damage passes through and affects  XXXXcharnameXXXX.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can use Reflection indefinitely, so long as it isn&#39;t overcome by superior force. After The first time  XXXXcharnameXXXX &#39;s reflection is breached, it becomes inactive for one hour for each rank of intensitity the assaulting for was then that of the reflection</p>",


	"resistance (emotion attacks)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX has increased resistance to emotion-based attacks. Such attacks include Emotion Control, Hallucinations, Domination, and attacks aimed at their Intuition.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore attacks with Intensities less than that of their power rank/willpower (depending on which is greater), and may reduce damage from higher level attacks by  XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s resistance.</p>",


	"resistance (energy attacks)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX has an increased resistance to any energy broadcast against them, whether artificial, natural, or Power-based. Such attacks include Light, Heat, Flame, Plasma, Hard radiation, Electricity, Vibration, Sonics, Cold, and Kinetic Bolts (most of the Energy Emission category).  XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore attacks with Intensities less than  XXXXcharnameXXXX Power rank and may reduce higher level attacks by  XXXXcharnameXXXX own Power Rank.</p>",


	"resistance (magic attacks)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX has increased resistance to magic based attacks.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore attacks with Intensities less than  XXXXcharnameXXXX Power rank and may reduce higher level attacks by  XXXXcharnameXXXX own Power Rank.</p>",


	"resistance (mental attacks)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX has increased resistance to psychic assualts and attacks aimed at  XXXXcharnameXXXX mind and/or neural system. Such attacks include psionics, neural manipulation, and any other attacks aimed at the mind or they&#39;re willpower.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore attacks with Intensities less than  XXXXcharnameXXXX Power rank and may reduce higher level attacks by  XXXXcharnameXXXX own Power Rank.</p>",


	"resistance (physical attack)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX has an increased resistance to any physical attack (blunt or kinetic). This includes brute force, chemical weapons, biochemicals, disease, hostile environments, and temperature extremes. The XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore any physical attacks with Intensities less than that of the Power rank, and may reduce damage from higher level attacks by XXXXcharnameXXXX own Power Rank.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore attacks with Intensities less than XXXXcharnameXXXX Power rank and may reduce higher level attacks by  XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s own Power Rank.</p>",


	"resistance (power manipulation)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX has increased resistance to attacks that directly affect XXXXcharnameXXXX Powers. Such attacks include Weakness Creation, Power Control, Power Domination, Magic Control, and Magical Domination.</p>

	<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore any attack whose rank is less than that of  XXXXcharnameXXXX power rank. XXXXcharnameXXXX may reduce the effectiveness of higher level attacks by XXXXcharnameXXXX own Power Rank.</p>",


	"resistance (Vampirism)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX has increased resistance to any vampiric-type attacks. Such attacks include forms of Psi, Bio, Energy, Magic, and Power Vampirism.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore any vampiric attack whose rank is less than this Power&#39;s rank. XXXXcharnameXXXX can reduce The effectiveness of the vampire&#39;s attack by deducting  XXXXcharnameXXXX Power Rank from the vampiric attack&#39;s Power rank.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can ignore attacks with Intensities less than  XXXXcharnameXXXX own Power rank and may reduce higher level attacks by  XXXXcharnameXXXX own Power Rank.</p>"
