$aarPowDetection = [
	"360&deg; perception" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX is aware of his local environment, allowing  XXXXcharnameXXXX to perceive their entire local surrounds as if  XXXXcharnameXXXX had a three -</strong>dimensional map in their head. Because of this,  XXXXcharnameXXXX is not reliance on  XXXXcharnameXXXX eyes for perceiving their surroundings. Thus, it is enarly impossible to blindside or to sneak up on  XXXXcharnameXXXX. as they have in effect a 360 degree field of &#34;vision&#34;.  XXXXcharnameXXXX is immune to the effects of invisibility and darkness unless such effects directly effect the mind.</p>",


	"abnormal sensitivity" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s senses function in their normal manner but their normal range of sensitivity is altered. The senses detect what they normally cannot and cannot detect what they normally can.</p>

	<p>This affects either vision or hearing. the former case,  XXXXcharnameXXXX sees infrared and ultraviolet light, radio waves, and radiation. In the latter case,  XXXXcharnameXXXX hears e  XXXXcharnameXXXX tremely high and low pitches.</p>

	<p>This may be considered a handicap human characters while for aliens this could be a fact of life. A XXXXcharnameXXXX can turn it into an advantage by devising a mean.of negating the senses of his adversary that doesn&#39;t hinder his own altered senses.</p>",


	"circular vision (360)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can see 360 degrees around  XXXXcharnameXXXX.</p>",


	"danger sense" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can sense moments before a dangerous situation is about to occur, and usually from what direction such danger will emminate. Simply put, sense danger notifies  XXXXcharnameXXXX when they are about to be endangered. It is a limited form of Precognition. This power is often given different names, and like most mental powers, varies greatly from person to person. Spider -</strong>Man&#39;s danger sense is called his &#39;spider -</strong>sense&#39;, and alerts him when danger is near, though he does not always know the specifics of the danger. Additionally, this sense may warn when others are lying to them if such lies would endanger the  XXXXcharnameXXXX.</p>",


	"detection (biological life)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect and identify biological, genetic and/or related phenomena.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect and discern the differences between both comple  XXXXcharnameXXXX and simple life forms. As such, they can sense the difference between human and an anemba, a cat and a dog or a human and a mutant.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can identify the those they&#39;ve met before; identify the specific persons with an Amazing rank; and on an Unearthly FEAT, provided  XXXXcharnameXXXX knows of the user,  XXXXcharnameXXXX can identify the actual possessor of the psionic power.</p>",


	"detection (energy)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect and identify energy and related phenomena.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can only detect actual energy, not potential energy (it couldn&#39;t detect a bomb until it e  XXXXcharnameXXXX plodes, for example). Likewise, while it can detect the energies consciously emitted by superhumans, it cannot detect the super humans themselves.</p>",


	"detection (extra dimensional)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can sense across dimensional barriers and see things existing in other dimensions. These include Asgard, the Astral Plane, Avalon, the Dark Dimension, the Demon Dimension, etc. The power rank number equals the number of different dimensions into which  XXXXcharnameXXXX can see.</p>",


	"detection (magic)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect and identify magic and its effects.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect both magic in actual use and in potential. As such, this is another way to detect mutants, although it cannot differentiate them from normal magic-users.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can identify the past use of magic, identifys the caster if familiar to them, and in some instances identify the actual spell.</p>",


	"detection (power)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect and identify superhuman Powers and can function as &#34;Mutant Detection.&#34; XXXXcharnameXXXX can also identify specific superhumans by their characteristic Powers (an Unearthly FEAT).  XXXXcharnameXXXX can identify the presence of previously invoked power when e  XXXXcharnameXXXX amining former targets of Power of a Good Intensity or greater within there sphere of detection.</p>",


	"detection (psionic)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect and identify psionic Power and related phenomena. It can detect both actual psionics and the potential to use them. As such, this is the last way to detect mutants.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can identify the past use of psionics on a living subject on an E  XXXXcharnameXXXX cellent Intensity FEAT; identify the specific psionic Power on an Amazing Intensity FEAT; and on an Unearthly FEAT, provided  XXXXcharnameXXXX knows of the user,  XXXXcharnameXXXX can identify the actual possessor of the psionic power.</p>",


	"detection (weakness)" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect flaws and stress points in a target. This doesn&#39;t guarantee  XXXXcharnameXXXX can exploit this knowledge, though. The rank determines the types of weaknesses  XXXXcharnameXXXX can sense.</p>",


	"dimensional vision" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can sense across the dimensional barrier and see things existing in other dimensions and/or vibratory planes</p>",


	"Elemental Sense" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can immediately identify the elemental compostion and structure of an object and determine structural weaknesses (if any) on contact with the object. This is a subconscious, intuitive.</p>",


	"hyper-hearing" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect e  XXXXcharnameXXXX tremely faint sounds and unusual frequencies.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can identify objects by the sounds they emit. Because of the sensitivity of  XXXXcharnameXXXX hearing,  XXXXcharnameXXXX is more vulnerable to sonic attacks (which receive a +1RS against  XXXXcharnameXXXX.</p>",


	"hyper-olfactory" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect the presence of minute traces of substances and accurately identify them by smell. This Power is continually functioning</p>",


	"hyper-taste" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect the presence of minute traces of substances and accurately identify them by taste. This Power is continually functioning;  XXXXcharnameXXXX has learned to ignore unpleasant smells. If he loses  XXXXcharnameXXXX ability to mask out nasty odors, he&#39;ll be so distracted (and possibly sickened) by the intruding odors that he loses 1 endurance rank per day the condition persists</p>",


	"hyper-touch" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX possesses an Enhanced sense of touch that permits  XXXXcharnameXXXX to detect e  XXXXcharnameXXXX tremely fine surface details and to identify materials by their surface &#34;feel.&#34;</p>",


	"microscopic vision" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s eyes can focus on e  XXXXcharnameXXXX tremely minute targets, objects too small for normal vision to perceive. This Power functions in two stages. The first is light magnification;  XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s eyes function as normal microscopes. This allows  XXXXcharnameXXXX to see things as small as chromosomes. Beyond this level, light no longer carries information. The second stage of this Power is a variation of Clairvoyance that permits  XXXXcharnameXXXX to see miniature, rather than distant, targets</p>",


	"radar sense" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can gain a three -</strong>dimensional picture of his surroundings through the use of electromagnetic waves.  XXXXcharnameXXXX both emits and senses these waves.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can use the Power to locate and identify targets by their characteristic echoes.</p>
		<br>
	Because of  XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s sensitivity to electromagnetic waves,  XXXXcharnameXXXX has an increased vulnerability to electrical and magnetic attacks; these may temporarily negate Radarsense.</p>",


	"shadow sight" => "<p>Unlike most people who walk the Earth,  XXXXcharnameXXXX is at home in the shadows. As such  XXXXcharnameXXXX is not hindered by the absence of light as others might be and can see perfectly well regardless of how dark it is, natural or otherwise.</p>",


	"sonar" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can gain a three-dimensional picture of his environment through the use of soundwaves. The Power allows  XXXXcharnameXXXX to locate and identify targets by the way they reflect sound.
</p><p>
	There are two ways this Power can operate. Passive Sonar utilizes existing sound. Active Sonar uses special sounds emitted by  XXXXcharnameXXXX (this is how bats and dolphins do it). The latter form requires a special adaptation of  XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s voice; otherwise there is no real difference between them. Because of the special sensitivity of  XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s hearing,  XXXXcharnameXXXX is vulnerable to sonic attacks.</p>",


	"temporal sensitivity" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s physical senses function in such a way as to be able to &#39;perceive&#39; actions and events regardless of the rate, speed, or temporal factor in which such events might unfold. Likewise  XXXXcharnameXXXX physical senses can now sense/detect when extra-ordinary temporal events are occurring. This sensitivity may allow  XXXXcharnameXXXX a limited amount of post/precognitive abilities.</p>",


	"telescopic vision" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s eyes can focus on e  XXXXcharnameXXXX tremely distant targets, objects too far away for the unaided eye to perceive.  XXXXcharnameXXXX eyes function as normal binoculars. This allows  XXXXcharnameXXXX to see things regardless of distant so long as they aren&#39;t obstructed by the curvature of the planet, light pollution, etc.</p>",


	"thermal vision" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can see infrared light and heat images. This allows  XXXXcharnameXXXX to see in the dark, perceive temperature differences (especially those left by a living person&#39;s contact with an object), and partially see through solids. In the last case,  XXXXcharnameXXXX can only see the heat patterns of objects touching the other side of the barrier.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can judge the temperature of a target by its thermal color.  XXXXcharnameXXXX has an increased risk of being blinded by strong heat sources, even those that don&#39;t affect normal vision (-1R). Thermal vision may be a consciously-activated mode or the XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s normal means of vision.</p>",


	"tracking" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect and follow the tracks left by a specific target.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can detect environmental and spatial disturbances with the result that at high ranks  XXXXcharnameXXXX can actually track across deep space.</p>",


	"True Sight" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can see the correct image of a target, despite any attempts at concealment or disguise it. This Power can penetrate any means of hiding something&#39;s true nature, whether physical, psionic, illusionary, or power-based. True Sight can penetrate any disguise at or below its rank. Range is limited to one area unless the Power is coupled with a Power that e  XXXXcharnameXXXX tends his vision (Telescopic Vision, for example). The Power may be automatic or deliberate.</p>",


	"ultraviolet vision" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can see ultraviolet light. Because UV light isn&#39;t as readily absorbed by water as normal light, this Power enables  XXXXcharnameXXXX to see clearly through fog and at greater distance in the water (+1rs).  XXXXcharnameXXXX can also see the dim light given off by radioactive materials.  XXXXcharnameXXXX cannot actually &#34;see in the dark&#34;but only if UV light is present. The effect is the same when seen by normal people.  XXXXcharnameXXXX has an increased risk of being blinded by strong UV sources, like black lights and radiation.</p>",


	"x-ray vision" => "<p>This is commonly called &#34;x-ray vision&#34; but is not actually based on the emission of x-rays.  XXXXcharnameXXXX can see through any solid with the exception of lead; the effect is as if the obscuring material were transformed to clear glass. If this Power is interfered with by outside forces,  XXXXcharnameXXXX may perceives everything as a transparent outline."
];



$aarPowEnergyControl = [
	"catalytic control" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can control the speed at which chemical reactions occur. XXXXcharnameXXXX can increase or decrease the energies emitted or drained in such reactions by XXXXcharnameXXXX Power rank number. For example, XXXXcharnameXXXX could increase the heat, emitted by exothermic reactions like oxidation; XXXXcharnameXXXX could also increase the chilling effect of endothermic reactions. XXXXcharnameXXXX can increase or decrease the speed or rate at which reactions occur, like stopping iron from dissolving in acid or causing steel to rapidly transform into rust. XXXXcharnameXXXX can also develop a variety of Power stunts:</p>
