	"coldshaping" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can control any force that actively decreases the temperature of something else. This can be used to increase or decrease the Cold&#39;s Intensity by this Power&#39;s rank number. This function overlaps both Heat and Cold Generation but differs in that this Power cannot alter the natural temperature of a target or alter local temperatures to suit XXXXcharnameXXXX&#39;s whims.<br >
