	 XXXXcharnameXXXX can shape fields of intense cold and produce useful results. Ice Generation is a form of this Power. XXXXcharnameXXXX can create shapes of rapidly-formed ice that XXXXcharnameXXXX can use in a variety of Power stunts. XXXXcharnameXXXX can also develop variations on Ice Generation that use other materials present in XXXXcharnameXXXX local atmosphere. Such substances include carbon dio XXXXcharnameXXXX ide (even more slippery than ice, and the fog can knock people out), nitrogen, o XXXXcharnameXXXX ygen (potentially dangerous since a concentration of it can make normal flames e XXXXcharnameXXXX plode), and the inert gases (an Amazing FEAT, since there are so few of these present in Earth&#39;s atmosphere-but on other planets, not so tough).</p>",


	"darkforce manipulation" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can generate and control the extra-dimensional energy-form known as &#34;Darkforce.&#34;This resembles a tangible, impenetrable shadow and possesses several unique characteristics that XXXXcharnameXXXX can use to develop Power Stunts:
