	"electrical manipulation" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX can create electrical streams that can do Rank damage. XXXXcharnameXXXX can project the electricity through any conductive medium, such as air, water, or metal, at Power rank range. If the player chooses, XXXXcharnameXXXX can gain +2RS to his damage by choosing to limit his range to contact only. In this case, the range can be e XXXXcharnameXXXX tended by conducting the Power through solid conductors like metal. Electricity comes in various forms:
	</p>
